<h2 class="h1 headline">Shelf insert Case</h2>
<p>The Case shelf insert is a versatile element for customised bathroom design. Case loosens up a style, creates accents in a different colour and is the perfect stage for personal design and decoration ideas. It is available in four different wood and concrete décors.</p>
